### 2.1  Create Destination — Paris
# @name createDest1
POST {{catalog}}/Destinations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Paris, Eiffel Quarter",
  "country": "France",
  "city": "Paris",
  "region": "Île-de-France",
  "description": "Cultural hub with iconic landmarks and world-class cuisine."
}

###

### 2.2  Create Destination — Tokyo
# @name createDest2
POST {{catalog}}/Destinations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tokyo Central",
  "country": "Japan",
  "city": "Tokyo",
  "region": "Kanto",
  "description": "Vibrant metropolis blending tradition and modernity."
}

