###  SECTION 3 — TRAVELLERS
### ============================================================

### 3.1  Create Traveller — John Smith
# @name createTraveller1
POST {{catalog}}/Travellers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "john.smith@company.com",
  "phone": "+49-151-12345678",
  "userID": "john.smith@company.com",
  "type_code": "FF",
  "status_code": "A",
  "addressType_code": "H"
}

###

### 3.2  Create Traveller — Priya Sharma
# @name createTraveller2
POST {{catalog}}/Travellers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Priya",
  "lastName": "Sharma",
  "email": "priya.sharma@company.com",
  "phone": "+91-98765-43210",
  "userID": "priya.sharma@company.com",
  "type_code": "EX",
