### ============================================================
###  SECTION 6 — $EXPAND CALLS (Dependent Entity Reads)
### ============================================================

### 6.1  Travellers + all Visited Locations
GET {{catalog}}/Travellers
  ?$expand=locations
Accept: application/json

###

### 6.2  Travellers + Locations + each Location's Destination
GET {{catalog}}/Travellers
  ?$expand=locations($expand=destination)
Accept: application/json

###

### 6.3  Travellers with $select + nested $expand + $select
GET {{catalog}}/Travellers
  ?$select=ID,firstName,lastName,fullName,status_code
  &$expand=locations($select=travelFrom,travelTo,notes;$expand=destination($select=name,country,city))
Accept: application/json

###

### 6.4  Single Traveller with full expand
GET {{catalog}}/Travellers({{travellerId}})
  ?$expand=locations($expand=destination),type,status,addressType
Accept: application/json

###

### 6.5  Travelled Locations with Destination expanded
GET {{catalog}}/TravelledLocations
  ?$expand=destination
  &$orderby=travelFrom desc
Accept: application/json

###

### 6.6  Travelled Locations with both Traveller and Destination
GET {{catalog}}/TravelledLocations({{locationId}})
  ?$expand=traveller($select=firstName,lastName,fullName),destination($select=name,country,city)
Accept: application/json

###

### 6.7  Filter active travellers + expand locations in 2025
GET {{catalog}}/Travellers
  ?$filter=status_code eq 'A'
  &$expand=locations($filter=travelFrom ge 2025-01-01;$orderby=travelFrom asc)
Accept: application/json

###

### 6.8  OData V2 — Travellers with locations expand
GET {{catalog_v2}}/Travellers?$expand=locations
Accept: application/json

###

### 6.9  UserManagement — Users with Roles expanded
GET {{usermgmt}}/Users
  ?$expand=roles($expand=role)
Accept: application/json

###

### 6.10  Single User with Role detail
GET {{usermgmt}}/Users({{userId}})
  ?$expand=roles($select=role_ID;$expand=role($select=name,description))
Accept: application/json

###


