### ============================================================
###  SECTION 10 — ADDITIONAL FILTERS & QUERIES
### ============================================================

### 10.1  Filter travellers by status
GET {{catalog}}/Travellers?$filter=status_code eq 'A'
Accept: application/json

###

### 10.2  Filter locations in date range
GET {{catalog}}/TravelledLocations
  ?$filter=travelFrom ge 2025-01-01 and travelTo le 2025-12-31
  &$orderby=travelFrom asc
Accept: application/json

###

### 10.3  Search destinations by country
GET {{catalog}}/Destinations?$filter=country eq 'France'
Accept: application/json

###

### 10.4  Top 5 most recent locations
GET {{catalog}}/TravelledLocations
  ?$orderby=travelFrom desc
  &$top=5
  &$expand=destination($select=name,city)
Accept: application/json

###

### 10.5  Count travellers
GET {{catalog}}/Travellers/$count
Accept: text/plain

###

### 10.6  Count destinations
GET {{catalog}}/Destinations/$count
Accept: text/plain

###
